/* Editor 
 * 
 * Styling Editor means styling the Editor inside iframe container (riaswEditorIFrameContainer)
 * 
 * 1. Editor iframe container (default styling): 
 * 		.riaswEditorIFrameContainer - normal state styles: background-color, border, padding
 *
 * 2. hovered Editor iframe container (ie, mouse hover on editor)
 * 		.riaswEditorHover .riaswEditorIFrameContainer/riaswEditorIFrame - styles when mouse hover on the container
 * 
 * 3. focused Editor iframe container (ie, mouse focus on the editor pane)
 * 		.riaswEditorFocused .riaswEditorIFrameContainer/riaswEditorIFrame - styles when container focused
 * 
 * 3. disabled Editor iframe container 
 * 		.riaswEditorDisabled - editor's inner iframe container disable status styles: background, border
 */

